<div id="review_2396408167" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/2396408167" />
    <a title="sally♡" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/55216274-sally"><img alt="sally♡" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1624376131p2/55216274.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/2396408167?book_show_action=true">May 19, 2018</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="sally♡" class="user" itemprop="url" name="sally♡" href="/user/show/55216274-sally">sally♡</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Hardcover 9781250136121" href="/book/show/31625048-let-s-talk-about-love">review of another edition</a>


        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/55216274-sally?shelf=contemporary">contemporary</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/55216274-sally?shelf=lgbtqia">lgbtqia</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/55216274-sally?shelf=praise-for-diversity">praise-for-diversity</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/55216274-sally?shelf=female-empowerment">female-empowerment</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2396408167" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer816152146626555627">Let&apos;s talk about how cute this book is!<br/><br/>// Can we appreciate the tag on the cover: &quot;Alice is about to <u>ace</u> this whole dating thing&quot;?? 🤩<br/><br/>I adored Alice. She was a fun, lovable character who was her own person and proud of it. Black, beautiful, biromantic and asexual, she rocked this book.<br/><br/>Many other characters, however, I wanted to kill slowly and painfully. Like FEENIE. That ungrateful, self centered devil child deserved to DIE. Same with Alice&apos;s freaking terrible family -- her mom and dad were basi</span>
  <span id="freeText816152146626555627" style="display:none">Let's talk about how cute this book is!<br /><br />// Can we appreciate the tag on the cover: "Alice is about to <u>ace</u> this whole dating thing"?? 🤩<br /><br />I adored Alice. She was a fun, lovable character who was her own person and proud of it. Black, beautiful, biromantic and asexual, she rocked this book.<br /><br />Many other characters, however, I wanted to kill slowly and painfully. Like FEENIE. That ungrateful, self centered devil child deserved to DIE. Same with Alice's freaking terrible family -- her mom and dad were basically forcing her to be a lawyer and they almost disowned her when she told them she didn't want to study law -- and her horrible sister, who called her every day just to yell at Alice and make her feel sick about her life and who she is. Some family.<br /><br />The romance was so cute, SHIPSHIPSHIP! The rep was amazing -- love interest was Asian! Japanese, I think. Amazing.<br /><br />I absolutely recommend! If you're looking for a fluffy and lighthearted read, here it is. :)<br /><br />~<br /><br />Time to see what the hype is all about!!</span>
  <a data-text-id="816152146626555627" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


