              <span id="reviewTextContainer2477493938" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer10494141874039891339">✪✪✪1/2<br/><blockquote>
  <i>“Love shouldn’t hinge solely on exposing your physical body to another person. Love was intangible. Universal. It was whatever someone wanted it to be and should be respected as such.”</i>
